  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Brilliant sunlight flashes in a 60-foot radius centered on spot you can see within range. Each creature in that light must make a constitution saving throw, taking 12d6+12 fire damage and is blinded for 1 minute on a failed save. On a successful save, it takes half as much damage and isn't blinded by this jutsu.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above A-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and increase the damage by 1d6+1.</p>",
